I found this hotel to be far above average, and I would be absolutely thrilled to stay here in the future.	Overall, my stay was fine, but considering the cost of the room, I have had better value elsewhere in Vancouver.	As I said earlier, this was our second visit, and we would definitely consider staying again.	I often stay here for business as I'm a Marriott Platinum guest and need to keep points up.	Vancouver is beautiful and I can't wait to return in January for my next business trip.	I would hope that the rooms are rennovated before my next visit, but it wouldn't stop me.